@using ExploreJordan.Settings;
@using System.Security.Claims

@model ExploreJordan.ViewModels.CombinedViewModel
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<link href="~/csspop/deadsea.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Dead sea</title>
</head>
<body>
   
    <div class="Popular">
        <h2 style="text-align: center;margin-top:125px;">Dead Sea</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="style-0">
        <div class="style-1">
            <div class="style-2">
                <div class="style-3" data-ft="true">
                    <div class="style-4">
                        <div class="style-5">
                            <button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-6">
                                <picture class="style-7">
                                    <img src="~/img2/deadsea/1.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-11" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-12">
                                <picture class="style-13">
                                    <img src="~/img2/deadsea/2.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-17" />
                                </picture>
                            </button><button aria-label="See all photos" class="style-18">
                                <picture class="style-19">
                                    <img src="~/img2/deadsea/3.jpg" width="720" height="480" role="none" alt="" fetchpriority="high" class="style-23" />
                                </picture>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="style-27"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="style-28">
                <div class="style-29">
                    <section class="style-30">
                        <div data-automation="WebPresentation_ProductAboveTheFoldInfo" class="style-31">
                            <div class="style-32" data-ft="true">
                                <div class="style-33">
                                    <div class="style-34">
                                        <div class="style-35">
                                            <div class="style-36">About</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="style-37">
                                        <div class="style-38">
                                            <div class="style-39">
                                                <div class="style-40"><p>The Dead Sea is a unique and fascinating place. Here's some information about it, focusing on safe and appropriate content:<p>Location: Nestled between Jordan and Israel, the Dead Sea is the lowest point on Earth, located 1,400 feet below sea level.</p> <p>Salinity: With a salinity of approximately 34%, it is one of the saltiest bodies of water in the world, nearly 10 times saltier than the ocean. This high salt content prevents most life forms from thriving, hence the name "Dead Sea."</p><p>Unique Properties: The Dead Sea's natural buoyancy, thanks to its high salt content, allows people to effortlessly float and relax. Its mud is also known for its therapeutic properties, attracting visitors for mud baths and treatments.</p> <p>Natural Beauty: The Dead Sea is surrounded by stunning landscapes, including desert plains, mountains, and canyons. The unique contrast of the turquoise water against the barren landscape creates a breathtaking sight.</p> <p>Historical Significance: The Dead Sea has been a site of human activity for centuries. Archaeological evidence points to civilizations inhabiting the area as early as 10,000 BC. The Dead Sea Scrolls, ancient religious texts dating back to the 3rd century BC, were discovered near the shores of the sea.</p><p>Things to do: Visitors can enjoy swimming, floating, and mud baths in the Dead Sea. Hiking, exploring historical sites, and enjoying the scenic beauty are also popular activities.</p><p>Safety Tips: Due to the high salt content, avoid getting the Dead Sea water in your eyes and open wounds. Wash thoroughly after swimming.</p> <p>General Information:</p><p>Size: 1,400 km². Depth: 304 meters (maximum).Climate: Hot and dry.Languages: Arabic, Hebrew, English</p></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </section>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="conwrap">
        @if (Model != null)
        {
            @if (Model.Activities != null)
            {
                @foreach (var activity in Model.Activities)
                {
                    if (activity.City != null && activity.City.Trim().Equals("Dead sea", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer0">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@activity.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{activity.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@activity.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@activity.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Activities" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@activity.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Accommodations != null)
            {
                @foreach (var accommodation in Model.Accommodations)
                {
                    if (accommodation.City != null && accommodation.City.Trim().Equals("Dead sea", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@accommodation.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{accommodation.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@accommodation.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@accommodation.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD/Day</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Accommodation" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@accommodation.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }

            @if (Model.Tours != null)
            {
                @foreach (var tour in Model.Tours)
                {
                    if (tour.City != null && tour.City.Trim().Equals("Dead sea", StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
                    {
                        <div class="CarRentalContainer">
                            <div class="style-00">
                                <div class="style-01">
                                    <div class="style-02">
                                        <div class="style-03">
                                            <div class="style-05">
                                                <span class="style-06">
                                                    <span class="style-07">@tour.Name</span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="imagesize0">
                                            <img src="@($"{FileSettings.ImagesPath}/{tour.Cover}")" alt="Car Image" />
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-09">
                                            <div>@tour.Description</div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-052">

                                            <span class="style-053">
                                                <span class="style-054">@tour.Price</span>
                                                <span class="style-055">JD</span>
                                            </span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="style-051">
                                            <div class="style-056" data-testid="rc-itinerary-cta-button">
                                                <div class="style-057">
                                                    <a asp-controller="Tours" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@tour.Id" class="style-058">
                                                        <div class="style-059">View Deal</div>
                                                    </a>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    }
                }
            }
        }

    </div>
    
</body>
</html>